ops::bit::Shr::shr.doc:
Performs the `>>` operation.

# Examples

```
assert_eq!(5u8 >> 1, 2);
assert_eq!(2u8 >> 1, 1);
```

ops::bit::BitAnd::bitand.doc:
Performs the `&` operation.

# Examples

```
assert_eq!(true & false, false);
assert_eq!(true & true, true);
assert_eq!(5u8 & 1u8, 1);
assert_eq!(5u8 & 2u8, 0);
```

ops::bit::Shl::shl.doc:
Performs the `<<` operation.

# Examples

```
assert_eq!(5u8 << 1, 10);
assert_eq!(1u8 << 1, 2);
```

